name: kwantspectrum
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set name = "kwantspectrum" %}
{% set version = "0.1.0" %}


package:
  name: {{ name|lower }}
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  url: https://pypi.io/packages/source/{{ name[0] }}/{{ name }}/{{ name }}-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: 52281f913f33451de24a2e7d94f5b2eac2becc87f8408485e141fa70b3315c6c

build:
  number: 0
  noarch: python
  script: {{ PYTHON }} -m pip install . -vv

requirements:
  host:
    - pip
    - python >=3.5
  run:
    - kwant >=1.4
    - numpy
    - python >=3.5
    - scipy

test:
  imports:
    - kwantspectrum
    - kwantspectrum.tests
  commands:
    - pip check
  requires:
    - pip

about:
  home: https://gitlab.kwant-project.org/kwant/kwantspectrum
  summary: Adaptive band structure analyzer for Kwant leads
  license: BSD-2-Clause
  license_file: LICENSE.rst

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - basnijholt
